We are trying to use a web service to perform our new project creation.  While doing the creation we need the capability of setting the Issue Type Scheme, Workflow Scheme, Issue Type Screen Scheme, etc which is not currently available.  Is there any way to have these added to the SOAP or have the ability to define the schemes to be used during new project creation?

